        version = "0.0.3">

    <name>sketch-note-draw</name>
    <shortdescription>Zoomable drawing on infinite canvas</shortdescription>
    <description>Simple sketching program, with clean interface.

- Infinite canvas
- Zoom in/out
- Also usable with one hand (single thumb)
- Automatically saves current sketch with timestamp, when loading, or creating a new one.
- Undo support

Made it because I wanted a tool to make quick sketches / napkin-notes.
</description>
    <author href="http://solsort.com" email="sketch-note-draw@solsort.com">Rasmus Erik Voel Jensen (solsort.com)</author>
    <icon src="icon.png" />
    <!--splash src="www/assets/splash.png" /-->

